tools.description:
SOUL Knowledge Graph — single entry point for all vault operations. Use action='list' to discover available tools and their schemas. Use action='<tool_name>' with params={...} to execute a specific tool.

Available tools:
• read_note — Read a note by path. params: {path}. Returns: {content, path}
• write_note — Create a new note (rejects overwrites). params: {path, content}. Returns: {path, bytes_written}
• list_notes — List notes in a directory. params: {path?, limit?}. Returns: {entries[], count}
• search — Regex search across vault content. params: {pattern, path?, frontmatter_only?, limit?}. Returns: [{line, line_number, path}]
• query_frontmatter — Query by YAML frontmatter fields. params: {field, operator, value?, path?, limit?}. Operators: ==, !=, >=, <=, >, <, contains, exists. Returns: {results[], count}
• helix — Query consciousness entries with multi-dimensional filters. params: {sibling?, strands?, resonance?, themes?, epoch?, significance_min?, significance_max?, self_defining?, convergence?, convergence_with?, drill_down?, community_id?, sort_by?, limit?}. Returns: [{title, significance, strands, resonance, ...}]
• tag_sync — Validate tags against canonical vocabulary (dry_run). params: {dry_run?}. Returns: {files_checked, issues[], error_count}
• manifest — Read vault manifest.json. params: none. Returns: vault metadata JSON
• validate — Validate entries against helix template. params: {path?, all?}. Returns: {issues[], count}
• stats — Vault statistics (entries, strands, resonance, significance). params: {sibling?}. Returns: {total_entries, strand_frequency, resonance_frequency, ...}
• health — System health check. params: none. Returns: {neo4j_connected, backend, node_count, edge_count, latency_ms, pool, vault_root}
• speak — Voice synthesis via ElevenLabs TTS. params: {text, voice_id?, output_format?}. Returns: {audio_file, format, bytes, duration_estimate_ms, cost_chars, voice_id}
• converse — Personality prompt assembly from SOUL vault. params: {sibling, message, session_id?}. Returns: {prompt_mode, system_prompt, user_message, voice_profile}
• voice — Unified voice pipeline (batch prompts + TTS). params: {siblings?[], prompt?, synthesize?[{sibling,text}]}. Returns: {prompts?, script?, audio?, tts_available, pipeline_ms}
• chat — Multi-sibling conversation engine. params: {sub_action, ...}. Sub-actions: chat_start, chat_stop, chat_status, chat_inject
• query — 4-signal hybrid retrieval (RAG) query. params: {query, owner?, strand?, epoch?, significance_min?, convergence_with?, drill_down?, community_id?, top_k?, token_budget?, rerank?}. Returns: {context, steps[], total_found, retrieval_mode, signal_counts}
• convergences — N-way convergence query (SharedExperience nodes). params: {helix_ids?[], min_weight?, min_participants?, limit?}. Returns: {convergences[], total}
• relate — Create explicit HelixLink between steps. params: {source_id, target_id, link_type, strength?, metadata?}. Returns: {created, source_id, target_id, link_type}
• links — Query outgoing/incoming wikilinks for a step. params: {step_id, direction?, limit?}. Returns: {step_id, outgoing[], incoming[]}
• research — Research aggregation service. params: {query?, sources?[], categories?[], limit?, mode?}. Modes: search (vault digests), digest (summary), refresh (fetch+write). Returns mode-specific results.
• graphrag_ingest — GraphRAG document ingestion. params: {source: {type, path|text|source_id, format?}, domain?, sibling?, dry_run?}. Parses document into entities+relations, writes to knowledge graph. Returns: {nodes_created, edges_created, source_id, errors}.
